  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23364890_94_2127-2201",
      "chapterUid": 94,
      "range": "2127-2201",
      "markText": "五星聚合一般要几十年乃至上百年才能出现一次。中国上一次出现聚合（间距＜30°）的时间是公元1921年。下一次出现五星聚合的时间则是公元2040年了。",
      "totalCount": 10752,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23364890&chapterUid=94&rangeStart=2127&rangeEnd=2201",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/36832c507164851a368ca1b?chapterUid=94&rangeStart=2127&rangeEnd=2201"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23364890_94_2473-2547",
      "chapterUid": 94,
      "range": "2473-2547",
      "markText": "风师谓之飞廉，雨师谓之荓翳（屏翳。荓，读píng；翳，读yì），云师谓之丰隆，日御谓之羲（xī）和，月御谓之望舒（这里是举例性质，见《广雅·释天》）",
      "totalCount": 2926,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23364890&chapterUid=94&rangeStart=2473&rangeEnd=2547",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/36832c507164851a368ca1b?chapterUid=94&rangeStart=2473&rangeEnd=2547"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23364890_94_17876-17930",
      "chapterUid": 94,
      "range": "17876-17930",
      "markText": "占星无疑是迷信。全世界所有的占星术都曾被统治阶层利用，作为欺人与自欺的工具，我们阅读古书，对此应该有所了解。",
      "totalCount": 2548,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23364890&chapterUid=94&rangeStart=17876&rangeEnd=17930",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/36832c507164851a368ca1b?chapterUid=94&rangeStart=17876&rangeEnd=17930"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23364890_97_7798-7877",
      "chapterUid": 97,
      "range": "7798-7877",
      "markText": "所谓气候变暖，其实未必伤害到人类狭隘的短期利益。反倒是气候变冷，才是各国政府需要积极反应、警惕对待的重大危机。当气候变冷，饥馑、战祸与政权倾覆也就接踵而至了。",
      "totalCount": 2505,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23364890&chapterUid=97&rangeStart=7798&rangeEnd=7877",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/36832c507164851a368ca1b?chapterUid=97&rangeStart=7798&rangeEnd=7877"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23364890_94_3220-3281",
      "chapterUid": 94,
      "range": "3220-3281",
      "markText": "古人把日月和金木水火土五星合起来称为七政或七曜（yào）。金木水火土五星是古人实际观测到的五个行星，它们又合起来称为五纬。",
      "totalCount": 2211,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23364890&chapterUid=94&rangeStart=3220&rangeEnd=3281",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/36832c507164851a368ca1b?chapterUid=94&rangeStart=3220&rangeEnd=3281"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23364890_95_5795-5874",
      "chapterUid": 95,
      "range": "5795-5874",
      "markText": "除了日月季年之外，还有更大的时间单位，这就是章、蔀（bù）、纪、元。十九年为一章，四章为一蔀（76年），二十蔀为一纪（1520年），三纪为一元（4560年）。",
